title: Braces
description: Braces shift teeth by applying pressure, which constricts blood flow to the surrounding tissue that holds those teeth in place.

title: Dental Drill
description: While the dental drill, sometimes known as a dental handpiece,it is also used for removing decay, polishing fillings, performing cosmetic dentistry, and altering prostheses.

title: Teeth Whitening
description: Bleaching method use carbamide peroxide which reacts with water to form hydrogen peroxide.

title: Dental floss
description: Dental floss is a cord of thin filaments used in interdental cleaning to remove food and dental plaque from between teeth, places a toothbrush has difficulty reaching, or is unable to reach

title: Prevention
description: The most important part of preventive dentistry is to brush teeth with fluoride toothpaste approved by ADA.
